Improvements
~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Every OSC sequence ("\033]") should have been a special prefix and
  postfix sequence for screen and tmux:

  screen =          "\033P" + OSC + control sequence + "\a\033\\"
  tmux =   "\033Ptmux:\033" + OSC + control sequence + "\033\\"

